_:N9d96deb16f02472e89832685fcec1360 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Keith Stewart KC was Advocate General for Scotland from October 2020 to July 2024.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"education\">Education</h3>\n<p>Keith attended Dirleton Primary School and George Heriot’s School, Edinburgh before going to Keble College, Oxford. Keith continued his education at the University of Edinburgh and the University of Strathclyde.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"career\">Career</h3>\n<p>Keith was called to the Bar in 1993 and took silk in 2011. He specialises in criminal law, and has advised in other matters including defamation and intellectual property.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"personal-life\">Personal Life</h3>\n<p>Keith lives in North Berwick and is married with two children.</p>\n" .
